ah]]'' || 5,387\n|-\n| [[Jerry Sloan]] || 5,385\n|-\n| [[Artis Gilmore]] || 5,342\n|-\n| [[Horace Grant]] || 4,721\n|-\n| [[Dave Greenwood]] || 4,222\n|-\n| [[Luol Deng]] || 4,078\n|-\n| [[Bob Love]] || 3,998\n|}\n{{column}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Most assists\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell2|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Player\n! style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell2|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Assists\n|-\n| [[Michael Jordan]] || 5,012\n|-\n| [[Scottie Pippen]] || 4,494\n|-\n| [[Kirk Hinrich]] || 3,811\n|-\n| [[Norm Van Lier]] || 3,676\n|-\n| ''[[Derrick Rose]]'' || 2,516\n|-\n| [[Reggie Theus]] || 2,472\n|-\n| [[John Paxson]] || 2,394\n|-\n| [[Bob Weiss]] || 2,008\n|-\n| [[Tom Boerwinkle]] || 2,007\n|-\n| [[Toni Kuko\u010d]] || 1,840\n|}\n{{columns-end}}\n{{columns-start|num=3}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Most steals\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell2|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Player\n! style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell2|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Steals\n|-\n| [[Michael Jordan]] || 2,306\n|-\n| [[Scottie Pippen]] || 1,792\n|-\n| [[Kirk Hinrich]] || 857\n|-\n| [[Norm Van Lier]] || 724\n|-\n| [[Luol Deng]] || 639\n|-\n| [[Horace Grant]] || 587\n|-\n| ''[[Jimmy Butler]]'' || 583\n|-\n| [[Reggie Theus]] || 580\n|-\n| ''[[Joakim Noah]]'' || 481\n|-\n| [[Toni Kuko\u010d]] || 476\n|}\n{{column}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Most blocks\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell2|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Player\n! style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell2|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Blocks\n|-\n| [[Artis Gilmore]] || 1,029\n|-\n| [[Michael Jordan]] || 828\n|-\n| ''[[Joakim Noah]]'' || 803\n|-\n| [[Scottie 