zer]] (2,426)\n* 46. ''[[Tyson Chandler]]'' (2,397)\n* 47. [[John Mengelt]] (2,386)\n* 48. [[Luc Longley]] (2,326)\n* 49. [[Stacey King]] (2,278)\n* 50. [[Will Perdue]] (2,264)\n{{columns-end}}\n\n;Other statistics (regular season) (as of the end of the 2018\u201319 season)<ref name=\"basketball-reference1\"/>\n{{columns-start|num=3}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Most minutes played\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell2|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Player\n! style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell2|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Minutes\n|-\n| [[Michael Jordan]] || 35,887\n|-\n| [[Scottie Pippen]] || 30,269\n|-\n| [[Jerry Sloan]] || 24,798\n|-\n| [[Kirk Hinrich]] || 23,545\n|-\n| [[Luol Deng]] || 22,882\n|-\n| [[Bob Love]] || 22,073\n|-\n| [[Norm Van Lier]] || 19,122\n|-\n| [[Horace Grant]] || 18,204\n|-\n| ''[[Joakim Noah]]'' || 16,858\n|-\n| [[Artis Gilmore]] || 16,777\n|}\n{{column}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Most rebounds\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell2|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Player\n! style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell2|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Rebounds\n|-\n| [[Michael Jordan]] || 5,836\n|-\n| [[Tom Boerwinkle]] || 5,745\n|-\n| [[Scottie Pippen]] || 5,726\n|-\n| ''[[Joakim Noah]]'' || 5,387\n|-\n| [[Jerry Sloan]] || 5,385\n|-\n| [[Artis Gilmore]] || 5,342\n|-\n| [[Horace Grant]] || 4,721\n|-\n| [[Dave Greenwood]] || 4,222\n|-\n| [[Luol Deng]] || 4,078\n|-\n| [[Bob Love]] || 3,998\n|}\n{{column}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Most assists\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell2|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Player\n! style=\"text-align:center; {{NBA color cell2|Chicago Bulls}};\"|Assists\n|-\n| [[Micha